    • getFullSnapshot

      public DoorBase getFullSnapshot()
      Gets a full copy of this DoorBase.

      A full copy includes a full copy of doorOwners. If this is not needed, consider using getPartialSnapshot() instead as it will be faster.

      Returns:
      A full copy of this DoorBase.

    • getPartialSnapshot

      public DoorBase getPartialSnapshot()
      Gets a full copy of this DoorBase.

      A partial copy does not include the doorOwners. If these are needed, consider using getFullSnapshot() instead.

      Returns:
      A partial copy of this DoorBase.
